    <script type="text/javascript">
        function LoginPage_OnLoad() {

            document.getElementById('screenResolution').value = "'" + screen.width + 'x' + screen.height + "'";

            //focus redirection
            var loginTextBox = window.document._all("LoginTextBox");
            var LoginPanel = window.document._all("LoginPanel");
            if (typeof (loginTextBox) != 'undefined' && loginTextBox != null) {
                LoginPanel.style.display = "";
                loginTextBox.focus();
            }
        }

        var key;

        function GetRandomSalt(callback) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "LoginPage.aspx/GetRandomSalt",
                data: "{}",
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                async: "true",
                success: function (randomSalt) {
                    callback(randomSalt.d);
                }
            });
        }

        function ValidateForm(sender) {
            try {
                if (!Page_ClientValidate()) {
                    window.focus();
                    return false;
                }

                sender.disabled = true;

                if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginSSOButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginSSOButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SaveButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("CancelButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(ChangePasswordCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("AskQuestions_SubmitQuestionsButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("AskQuestions_cancelQuestionsButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(AnswerSecurityQuestionsCallback);
            }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_BtnSubmit")) {
                    document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_btnCancel").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(SetupSecurityQuestionsCallback);
                }
            }
            finally {
                return false;        //ensure no postback
            }
        }

        function SwitchOffSsoValidation() {
            if (!/\S+/.test(window.document._all("LoginSSOTextBox").value) &&
                !/\S+/.test(window.document._all("PasswordSSOTextBox").value) &&
                /\S+/.test(window.document._all("NetworkSSOTextBox").value)) {
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("LoginSSOTextBoxValidator");
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("PasswordSSOTextBoxValidator");
            }
        }

        $(function () {
            if (T360.IsMSIE7OrLess()) {
                $(window).resize(function () { $('.Document').height($('.Document').parent().height()); });
                $(window).resize();
                $('.DisclaimerText').css('position', 'absolute');
            }
            if ($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height()) {
                $(window).resize(function () {
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height(0);
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height());
                });
                $(window).resize();
            }
            if ($('td.tdCenter').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdCenter').offset().top) {
                $('div.accountAgreement').addClass('eqie10');
            }
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        window.IsMainFrame = true;

        window.showCustomPrintMenu = function (links, target) {
            var dic = JsonFormatter.deserialize(links);
            var printMenu = $('#customPrintMenu');
            printMenu.empty();
            var ul = $("<ul>").appendTo(printMenu);
            for (var link in dic) {
                var li = $("<li>").css("display", "block").appendTo(ul);
                var ahref = $("<a>" + link.toString() + "</a>").attr("href", "javascript:void(0)").appendTo(li);
                var func = new Function('return this.' + dic[link]);
                var proxyFunc = $.proxy(func, target);
                ahref.on('click', proxyFunc);
            }
            printMenu.show();
            if (window.event.stopPropagation) {
                window.event.stopPropagation();
            } else {
                window.event.cancelBubble = true;
            }
        };

        window.sysToolbarInit = function (contentFrame) {
            var setupButton = function (name, funcs, uniqueId) {
                var button = $("#" + uniqueId);
                button.off('click');
                if (typeof funcs[name] === 'function') {
                    var proxyFunc = $.proxy(funcs[name], contentFrame);
                    button.on('click', proxyFunc);
                    button.show();
                } else {
                    button.hide();
                }
            };

            var contentFrameSupportsButtons = contentFrame != null && contentFrame.sysToolbarFuncs != null;
            var funcs = contentFrameSupportsButtons ? contentFrame.sysToolbarFuncs : [];

            setupButton('print', funcs, 'sysToolbarPrint');
            setupButton('email', funcs, 'sysToolbarEmail');
        };

      
        function getCountOfTabs() {
            var key = getTabCountKey();

            if (window.localStorage[key] == undefined) {
                window.localStorage[key] = 0;
            }

            return parseInt(window.localStorage[key]);
        }

        function setCountOfTabs(val) {        
            window.localStorage[getTabCountKey()] = val;
        }

        $(document).first().ready(function () {
            if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") {

                if (!window.sessionStorage.isLogged) {
                            
                    if (getCountOfTabs() > 0) {                    
                        window.sessionStorage.isLogged = true;
                    } else {                        
                        toolBar.logOff();
                    }
                }

                setCountOfTabs(getCountOfTabs() + 1);            
            }
        });

        $(window).first().one("beforeunload", function () {
            if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") {
                setCountOfTabs(getCountOfTabs() - 1);
            }
        });


        $('#DocumentIFrame').on('load', function () {
            window.IframeAfterLoadSeconds = (new Date()).getTime();
            window.IframePageLoadTimeSeconds = (window.IframeAfterLoadSeconds - window.IframeBeforeLoadSeconds) / 1000;
        });

    </script>

                    return false;

                }

            }

            updateSubmitButtonStatus();

                    function IsSelectedItemFeesExpensesTemplate()
                    {
                        for (var i=0; i< document.mainForm.length; i++)
                        {
                            var elementType=document.mainForm.elements[i].type;
                            var elementName=document.mainForm.elements[i].name;
                            var elementDisabled =document.mainForm.elements[i].disabled;

                            if(elementType=='checkbox' && elementName.search('chkSelect')!=-1 && elementDisabled==false)
                            {
                                if(document.mainForm.elements[i].checked)
                                {
                                    return eval(document.mainForm.elements[i].parentElement.getAttribute('IsFeesExpenses'));
                                }
                            }
                        }

                        return false;
                    }

                    function toggleAllSelected(val)
                    {
                        for (var i=0; i< document.mainForm.length; i++)
                        {
                            var e = document.mainForm.elements[i];
                            if(e.type=='checkbox' && e.name.search('chkSelect')!=-1 && e.disabled==false ) {
                                if (e.checked != val) {
                                    SetSelectedItemsCurrencyID(e.parentElement.getAttribute('CurrencyIDs'), val);
                                    e.checked=val;
                                   updateSelected(e, false);
                                }
                            }
                        }

                        updateSelectedItems();
                    }

                    function checkSelected()
                    {
                        return document.getElementById('SelectedItems').value.length > 0;
                    }

                    function checkProxySelected()
                    {
                        return document.getElementById('SelectedProxyCounter').value > 0;
                    }

                    function getSelectedTotal(actCode){
                        var netTotal = 0;
                        for (var i=0; i< document.mainForm.length; i++)
                        {
                            var elementType=document.mainForm.elements[i].type;
                            var elementName=document.mainForm.elements[i].name;
                            var elementDisabled =document.mainForm.elements[i].disabled;

                            if(elementType=='checkbox' && elementName.search('chkSelect')!=-1 && elementDisabled==false)
                            {
                                if(document.mainForm.elements[i].checked)
                                {
                                    var check = actCode == 'QUICK_REJECT_INVOICE' && (document.mainForm.elements[i].parentElement.getAttribute('IsInvoiceReadOnly') == '1');
                                        if (!check) {
                                            netTotal = eval(netTotal) + parseFloat(changeCurToJSSeparators(document.mainForm.elements[i].parentElement.getAttribute('NetTotal')));
                                        }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                        return netTotal;
                    }

                    function getSelectedPrefTotal(){
                        var netTotal = 0;
                        for (var i=0; i< document.mainForm.length; i++)
                        {
                            var elementType=document.mainForm.elements[i].type;
                            var elementName=document.mainForm.elements[i].name;
                            var elementDisabled =document.mainForm.elements[i].disabled;

                            if(elementType=='checkbox' && elementName.search('chkSelect')!=-1 && elementDisabled==false)
                            {
                                if(document.mainForm.elements[i].checked)
                                {
                                    netTotal = eval(netTotal) + parseFloat(changeCurToJSSeparators(document.mainForm.elements[i].parentElement.getAttribute('NetPrefTotal')));
                                }
                            }
                        }
                        return netTotal;
                    }

                    function SetSelectedItemsCurrencyID(currencyIDs, isChecked)
                    {
                        var selectedItemsCurrencyID = document._all('SelectedItemsCurrencyID').value;
                        if ( isChecked == true )
                        {
                            document._all('SelectedItemsCurrencyID').value = selectedItemsCurrencyID + '(' + currencyIDs + '),';
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            var index = selectedItemsCurrencyID.lastIndexOf('(' + currencyIDs + '),');
                            var newValue = '';
                            if (index >= 0)
                            {
                                if (index > 0)
                                    newValue = selectedItemsCurrencyID.substring(0, index);
                                var index1 = index + currencyIDs.length + 3;
                                if (index1 < selectedItemsCurrencyID.length)
                                    newValue = newValue + selectedItemsCurrencyID.substring(index1, selectedItemsCurrencyID.length);
                                document._all('SelectedItemsCurrencyID').value = newValue;
                            }
                        }
                    }

                    function updateProxySelectedCounter(e) {
                        if(eval(e.parentElement.getAttribute('isproxiedinvoicesview'))) {
                            if(e.checked) {
                                $('#SelectedProxyCounter').get(0).value++;
                            }
                            else {
                                $('#SelectedProxyCounter').get(0).value--;
                            }
                        }
                    }

                    function updateSelected(e, updateItems) {
                        updateProxySelectedCounter(e);
                        SetSelectedItemsCurrencyID(e.parentElement.getAttribute('CurrencyIDs'), e.checked);
                        if(updateItems) {
                            updateSelectedItems();
                        }
                    }

                    function updateSelectedItems()
                    {
                        var SelectedItems = document.getElementById('SelectedItems');
                        var listSelectedLines = SelectedItems.value;
                        SelectedItems.value='';
                        var values = listSelectedLines.split(',');

                        for (var i=0; i< document.mainForm.length; i++)
                        {
                            var e = document.mainForm.elements[i];
                            if(e.type == 'checkbox' && e.name.search('chkSelect')!=-1)
                            {
                                if(e.checked)
                                {
                                    if(SelectedItems.value.length==0) {
                                        SelectedItems.value = eval(e.parentElement.getAttribute('itemId'));
                                     }
                                    else {
                                        SelectedItems.value = SelectedItems.value + ',' + eval(e.parentElement.getAttribute('itemId'));
                                    }
                                }

                                for (j=0; j < values.length; j++)
                                {
                                    if (eval(values[j]) == eval(e.parentElement.getAttribute('itemId')))
                                        values[j]=0;
                                }
                            }
                        }

                        for (j=0; j < values.length; j++)
                        {
                            if (values[j]>0)
                            {

            <script language="javascript">
                
function InvoiceAction(parentForm, actionCode, netAmount, minAmount, isFeesOrExpenses, restoreAccrualStyle, currentAmount,reviewerId,previousStatus,reasonCodeDescription){
    this.ParentForm = parentForm;
    this.ActionCode = actionCode;
    this.NetAmount = netAmount;
    this.MinAmount = minAmount;
    this.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeesOrExpenses;
    this.AdjustedObject = "Invoice";
    this.RestoreAccrualStyle = restoreAccrualStyle;
    this.CurrentAmount = currentAmount;
    this.ReviewerId = reviewerId;
    this.PreviousStatus = previousStatus;
    this.ReasonCodeDescription = reasonCodeDescription;
    this.Results = new function()
        {
            this.toString = function()
                {
                    var a = new Array(encodeURIComponent(this.Narrative),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.BillCodeGroupBillCodeId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentType),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.IsFeesOrExpenses),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.RestoreAccrualStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.CurrentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReviewerId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.PreviousStatus),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReasonCodeDescription));
                    return a.join('|');
                }
        }
}
function quickAction(actionCode){
                    if(actionCode=='QUICK_APPROVE_INVOICE'
                            || actionCode=='QUICK_PRINT_AND_APPROVE_INVOICE'
                            || actionCode=='QUICK_REJECT_INVOICE'
                            || actionCode=='Delete Invoice Draft'
                            || actionCode=='NETWORK.SUBMIT_INVOICE_FOR_REPORTING'
                            || actionCode=='Submit Invoice For Review'
                            || actionCode=='NETWORK.SUBMIT_INVOICE_AS_PAID'
                            || actionCode=='Create Draft Invoice'
                            || actionCode=='PROXY_SELECTED_INVOICES')
                    {
                        if(actionCode=='QUICK_APPROVE_INVOICE'
                                    || actionCode=='QUICK_PRINT_AND_APPROVE_INVOICE'
                                    || actionCode=='PROXY_SELECTED_INVOICES'){
                            __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewQuickAction', actionCode);
                            return;
                        }

                        getReason(actionCode, function(result) {
                            if(result || actionCode=='Delete Invoice Draft'
                                        || actionCode=='NETWORK.SUBMIT_INVOICE_FOR_REPORTING'
                                        || actionCode=='Submit Invoice For Review'
                                        || actionCode=='NETWORK.SUBMIT_INVOICE_AS_PAID'
                                        || actionCode=='Create Draft Invoice'){
                                __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewQuickAction', actionCode);
                            }
                        });
                    }
                }

                function CurrentCurrency()
                {
                    var preferenceCurrency = document.getElementById('PreferenceCurrency').value;
                    if ( !isNaN(preferenceCurrency) && preferenceCurrency >= 0 )
                    {
                        return -1;
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        var curr = -1;
                        var currSymb = '';
                        result = true;
                        var arrayCurrId = document.getElementById('SelectedItemsCurrencyID').value.split(',');
                        for (i=0; i < arrayCurrId.length; i++)
                        {
                            if ( arrayCurrId[i].length > 2 )
                            {
                                if (curr == -1)
                                {
                                    curr = arrayCurrId[i].substring(1, arrayCurrId[i].length-1).split('|')[0]
                                    currSymb = arrayCurrId[i].substring(1, arrayCurrId[i].length-1).split('|')[1]
                                }
                                else
                                {
                                    if (curr!=arrayCurrId[i].substring(1, arrayCurrId[i].length-1).split('|')[0])
                                        result = false;
                                }
                            }
                        }
                        if (result == false)
                        {
                            return -1;
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            return currSymb;
                        }
                    }
                }

var matterInvoiceIDScript='';

                function getReason(actionCode, callback)
                {
                    var totalNewCurPage = getSelectedTotal(actionCode);
                    var totalOldCurPage = eval(document.getElementById('SelectedItemsTotalCurrentPage').value);
                    var totalAllPages = eval(document.getElementById('SelectedItemsTotal').value);
                    var total = totalAllPages + (totalNewCurPage-totalOldCurPage);

                    var prefTotalNewCurPage = getSelectedPrefTotal();
                    var prefTotalOldCurPage = eval(document.getElementById('SelectedItemsPrefTotalCurrentPage').value);
                    var prefTotalAllPages = eval(document.getElementById('SelectedItemsPrefTotal').value);
                    var prefTotal = prefTotalAllPages + (prefTotalNewCurPage-prefTotalOldCurPage);

                    var currenctCurrency = CurrentCurrency();
                    if (!isNaN(currenctCurrency) && currenctCurrency < 0)
                    {
                        total = prefTotal;
                    }
                    var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.mainForm, actionCode, total);

                    var SelectedItems = document.getElementById('SelectedItems');
                    var listSelectedLines = SelectedItems.value;
                    var values = listSelectedLines.split(',');
                    if(values.length == 1 && values[0].length > 0)
                    {
                        matterInvoiceIDScript = '&selected_invoice_ids=' + values[0];
                    }
                    else if(values.length > 1)
                    {
                        matterInvoiceIDScript = '&selected_invoice_ids=' + listSelectedLines;
                    }
                    if (!isNaN(currenctCurrency) && currenctCurrency < 0)
                    {
                        currenctCurrency = '$'
                    }
                    invoiceAction.CurrentCurrencySymbol = currenctCurrency;

                    var res = CheckReadOnlyInvoices(invoiceAction);

                    if (res) {
                            performAction(invoiceAction, function(ok){
                            if(ok){
                                window.mainForm.InvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                            }
                            if (typeof (callback) == 'undefined' || callback.constructor != Function)
                                throw 'Callback function in \'getReason\' is not specified';
                            callback.call(this, (ok != '' && ok != null))
                        });
                    }
                }

                var currentAction = null;
                function CheckReadOnlyInvoices(invoiceAction){
                    currentAction = new QuickAction();
                    return currentAction.CheckAction(invoiceAction, matterInvoiceIDScript);
                }

                function performAction(invoiceAction, callback)
                {
                    switch (invoiceAction.ActionCode)
                    {
                    // quick-reject invoices
                    case 'QUICK_REJECT_INVOICE': return OpenModalPageWithParams('\/Invoicing\/MatterInvoiceUI\/MatterInvoiceConfirmActionPage.aspx?__qry=5M2c1HUbLaJ0PjNzpkcEIGfnif4CsYI0LrniriHDQgF8YTytT98SNdUj3CEmLP9oU6Ug%2b%2btUdcWJuYEQnxLh8fWaLGdQa4ou9%2ftlGmxXd5QVwhiPjfjYUnSmk4MUpodr8RapU63xx0LEp7H4t%2fe5LKFQDadA2cpK69y24jey3xivygToSkq%2fAggHIVrB9PFD%2bZnSHvrujj%2fTjnCX%2biCTIA%3d%3d'+matterInvoiceIDScript, invoiceAction, 570, 329, callback);
                        break;
                    default:
                        callback(false);
                        break;
                    }
                }
            </script>

    <script type="text/javascript">
    function CheckAllAppeals() {
        var cbAll = document.getElementById("SelectAllCheckbox");
        var grid = document.getElementById("AllAppealDataGrid");
        var checked = cbAll.checked;
        $("input[id$=SelectCheckbox][type=checkbox]", grid).each(function () { this.checked = checked; });
    }

    function UpdateHeaderCheckBox() {
        var cbAll = document.getElementById("SelectAllCheckbox");
        var grid = document.getElementById("AllAppealDataGrid");
        var checked = false;
        var indeterminate = false;
        var first = true;
        $("input[id$=SelectCheckbox][type=checkbox]", grid)
            .each(function () {
                if (first) {
                    checked = this.checked;
                    first = false;
                }
                else if (this.checked != checked) {
                    indeterminate = true;
                    return false;
                }
            });
        cbAll.indeterminate = indeterminate;
        cbAll.checked = checked;
    }

    function checkAndInformUnsavedAdjNetToChanges() {
        var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
        if (changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount > 0)
            return 'You have unsaved adjustments to this invoice. If you leave this page you will lose you adjustments!';
    }

    var onBeforeUnloadFired = false; //IE twice fires occasionally fires onbeforeunload twice. manipulation with this variable solves problem. And also uses to 'cancel' onbeforeunload

    $(document).ready(function () {

        var getUnsavedChangesScript = function () {
            var handler = checkAndInformUnsavedAdjNetToChanges;
            return function () {
                this.onbeforeunload = null; // allow to call it once, then enables handler again in mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent

                var result = handler();
                if (result) {

                    mainFrameWindow.mainFrame._getPageDisabler().hide(); //PageDisabler already shown. Need to be hidden again

                    if (T360.IsMSIE9OrLess())
                        window.parent.event.returnValue = result;

                    return result;
                }
            };
        };

        var documentIFrameWindow = $('#DocumentIFrame', mainFrameWindow.document)[0].contentWindow;

        var onBeforeUploadHandler = function () {
            documentIFrameWindow.onbeforeunload = getUnsavedChangesScript();
        };
        /* enable onbeforeunload when user clicks on main menu */
        mainFrameWindow.mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent.attach(onBeforeUploadHandler);

        var $contentPackage = parent.$(':tyMetrix-t360contentPackage');
        $contentPackage.t360contentPackage('attachBeforeGoBackEventHandler', onBeforeUploadHandler);

        /* detach all handlers in order to keep mainmenu workable */
        documentIFrameWindow.onunload = function () {
            mainFrameWindow.mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent.free();
            $contentPackage.t360contentPackage('freeBeforeGoBackEventHandler');
        };

        $('div#InvoiceLineItemSection').on('click', 'tr.PagerStyle a', function () {
            ContainerUpdater.onceOnUpdate(function () {
                var $scrollContent = $('body.MatterInvoiceDetailPage #ContentPackagePage_ScrollContent');
                $scrollContent.animate({scrollTop: $scrollContent.scrollTop() + $('table#InvoiceLineItemDataGrid').offset().top - $scrollContent.offset().top}, 1);
            });
        });

        for (var i = 0, l = ePanel.length; i < l; i++) {
            $(ePanel[i]).off('collapsed expanded').on('collapsed expanded', function (event, epanel) {
                LineItemsGridMenuButtonClickProcessor.disablePanelsTabNavigation();
            });
        }
    });

        require(["jquery"], function ($) {
            $(document).on('beforePrint.pdfOutputModule', function (event, pageClientSideModel, printOption) {
                updateDetailsPageGridModel(pageClientSideModel);
                updateDetailsPageModel(pageClientSideModel);
                updateFacetsModel(pageClientSideModel, printOption);
            });
        });
    </script>

function InvoiceAction(parentForm, actionCode, netAmount, minAmount, isFeesOrExpenses, restoreAccrualStyle, currentAmount,reviewerId,previousStatus,reasonCodeDescription){
    this.ParentForm = parentForm;
    this.ActionCode = actionCode;
    this.NetAmount = netAmount;
    this.MinAmount = minAmount;
    this.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeesOrExpenses;
    this.AdjustedObject = "Invoice";
    this.RestoreAccrualStyle = restoreAccrualStyle;
    this.CurrentAmount = currentAmount;
    this.ReviewerId = reviewerId;
    this.PreviousStatus = previousStatus;
    this.ReasonCodeDescription = reasonCodeDescription;
    this.Results = new function()
        {
            this.toString = function()
                {
                    var a = new Array(encodeURIComponent(this.Narrative),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.BillCodeGroupBillCodeId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentType),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.IsFeesOrExpenses),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.RestoreAccrualStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.CurrentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReviewerId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.PreviousStatus),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReasonCodeDescription));
                    return a.join('|');
                }
        }
}

function doInvoiceConfirmableInvoiceRejectAction(actionCode, total, checkAdjustNetChanges){
    var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
    if((changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount != 0) && checkAdjustNetChanges) {
        __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewRequiereConfirmSaveChanges', actionCode);
    }
    else{
        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode, total);
        invoiceAction.NetTotal = total;
        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
            if(ok){
                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode);
            }    
        });
    }
}
                    function doInvoiceConfirmableAction(actionCode, total, postBackOnCancel, isFeeExpense, percentOfResponsibility)
                    {
                        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode, total);
                        invoiceAction.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeeExpense;
                        invoiceAction.NetTotal = total;
                        invoiceAction.PercentOfResponsibility = percentOfResponsibility >= 0 ? percentOfResponsibility : 1;
                        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
                        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
                            if(ok){
                                SetScrollTop();
                                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode);
                            }
                            else if(postBackOnCancel){
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewCancelAction', actionCode);
                            }
                        });                       
                    }
                    function doAdjustToSave(actionCode, postBackOnCancel, isFeeExpense)
                    {
                        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode);
                        invoiceAction.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeeExpense;
                        invoiceAction.NetTotal = 0;
                        invoiceAction.PercentOfResponsibility = 1;
                        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
                        var controlsToUpdate = getControlsToUpdate();
                        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
                            if(ok){
                                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);
                            }
                            else if(postBackOnCancel){
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewCancelAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);
                            }
                        });                       
                    }
function doSelectedLineItemUndoAction(actionCode){
    if(checkSelected()){
        var selectedLineItems = getSelectedLineItems();
        if(g_SelectedLineItemsCounter === 1){
            $("#" + selectedLineItems[0].id.replace('chkSelect', 'btnUndoLineItemActions')).click();
            return false;
        }
        var ok = confirm('Are you sure you want to undo all review actions for the selected line items?\r\n\r\nOnly your own review actions will be undone.');
        if(ok){
            SetScrollTop();
            var controlsToUpdate = null;
            actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);
        }
    }
    else{
            alert('No line items selected.');
    }
}
                function checkUnsavedAdjNetToChanges(isRequiredConfirm, actionCode)
                {
                      if(isRequiredConfirm)
                      {
                          var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
                          if(changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount > 0)
                          {
                              __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewRequiereConfirmSaveChanges', actionCode);
                              return false;
                          }
                      }
                      return true;
                }
                function onAdjustToCancelChangesButtonClick()
                {
                  var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
                  if(changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount > 0)
                  {
                      {Page_ValidationActive=false;__doPostBack('InvoiceReviewAction','CANCEL_ADJUST_NET_TO_CHANGES'); }
                  }
                  else
                  {
                      alert('No line items adjusted.');
                  }
                }
function doInvoiceConfirmableInvoiceReturnToVendorAction(actionCode){
             var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode);
            var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
            openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
            if(ok){
                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode);

        });
    }
function openDialog(invoiceAction, invoiceId, callback)
{
    var matterInvoiceIDScript = '&override_invoice=' + invoiceId;
    switch (invoiceAction.ActionCode){
        // reject
        case 'INVOICE.REJECT_MATTER_INVOICE':
            return OpenModalPageWithParams('\/Invoicing\/MatterInvoiceUI\/MatterInvoiceConfirmActionPage.aspx?__qry=5M2c1HUbLaJ0PjNzpkcEIGfnif4CsYI0LrniriHDQgGCEXoS01UH7kVqa2w%2fcxtc%2bEZ%2byXsow%2bZl8N7Ow1YRsMNdRzm5Uh%2fsT2Pv6g20vIa5AuMZSm9GvvkKBh%2booLFD2jxzsCWyyGtxVAO93aig6ZJRLXiXmUHaQxd%2f6M%2bXdD1gWz6yNVzRJzs64VPvBIQxTq6SzMlU3MZlwEqKaHZaepi4ODliOdP17QlX4Ja4qXI%3d', invoiceAction, 570, 329, callback);
            break;

    this.ParentForm = parentForm;
    this.ActionCode = actionCode;
    this.NetAmount = netAmount;
    this.MinAmount = minAmount;
    this.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeesOrExpenses;
    this.AdjustedObject = "Invoice";
    this.RestoreAccrualStyle = restoreAccrualStyle;
    this.CurrentAmount = currentAmount;
    this.ReviewerId = reviewerId;
    this.PreviousStatus = previousStatus;
    this.ReasonCodeDescription = reasonCodeDescription;
    this.Results = new function()
        {
            this.toString = function()
                {
                    var a = new Array(encodeURIComponent(this.Narrative),

                                      encodeURIComponent(this.RestoreAccrualStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.CurrentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReviewerId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.PreviousStatus),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReasonCodeDescription));
                    return a.join('|');
                }
        }
}

<body class="ModalBody MatterInvoiceConfirmActionPage" onkeypress="body_OnKeyPress(event);" onload="body_OnLoad(event);">

    <script type="text/javascript" language="javascript">
        function body_OnKeyPress(e) {
            var key;
            if (window.event || !e.which) { key = e.keyCode; }
            else if (e) { key = e.which; }
            if (key == 13 && !document._all('btnOK').disabled) {
                if (event.srcElement && (event.srcElement.id == "btnCancel" || event.srcElement.id == "txtNarrative")) {
                    return;
                }
                btnOK_OnClick();
            }
            if (key == 27) { btnCancel_OnClick(); }
        }
        function body_OnLoad() {
            window.returnValue = false; //done to make sure we return false if dialog is closed though the [X] button
            if (document.getElementById("ddlAdjustType") != null) {
                changeValidation(document.getElementById("ddlAdjustType")); //done to initialize correct regular expression in ecurrencytextbox object
            }
        }
        function btnCancel_OnClick() {
            window.returnValue = false;
            window.closeModal();
        }
        function ddlAdjustType_OnChange(ddlAdjustType) {
            changeValidation(ddlAdjustType);
            document.mainForm.txtAdjustmentAmount.value = "";
            updateCalculatedValue();

            moveFocusTo();
        }
        
        function removeNegation() {
            var oNegationList = document.forms["mainForm"].elements["ddlNegation"];
            for (x = oNegationList.options.length - 1; x >= 0; x--) {
                oNegationList.options.remove(x);
            }
        }
        
        function addNegation(newText, newValue) {
            var oNegationList = document.forms["mainForm"].elements["ddlNegation"];
            var newNegationListOption = document.createElement("OPTION");
            newNegationListOption.text = newText;
            newNegationListOption.value = newValue;
            oNegationList.options.add(newNegationListOption);
        }
        
        function updateNegation() {
            removeNegation();
            var AdjustByOrTo = document.getElementById("ddlAdjustByOrTo").value;
            if (AdjustByOrTo == "1") { //Adjust TO
                addNegation("-", "-1");
                addNegation("+", "1");
            }
            else if (AdjustByOrTo == "0") { //Adjust BY
                addNegation("-", "-1");
                if (hasPositiveAdjustments) {
                    addNegation("+", "1");
                }
            }
        }
        function updateCalculatedValue() {
            adjustmentAmount = changeCurToJSSeparators(document.getElementById("txtAdjustmentAmount").value);

            var adjustmentType = document.getElementById("ddlAdjustType").value;
            var AdjustByOrTo = document.getElementById("ddlAdjustByOrTo").value;
            var netTotal = parseFloat(window.dialogArguments.NetAmount);
            var percentOfResponsibility = window.dialogArguments.PercentOfResponsibility;
            var rate = parseFloat(window.dialogArguments.Rate);
            var unit = parseFloat(window.dialogArguments.Unit);

            var lblCalculatedAmount = document.getElementById("lblCalculatedAmount");
            var lblNetAmount = document.getElementById("lblNetAmount");

            var selectedItemsCount = window.dialogArguments.SelectedItemsCount;
            if (selectedItemsCount == null || selectedItemsCount === 'undefined') {
                selectedItemsCount = 1;
            }
            
            var nonZeroUnitsNetTotal = window.dialogArguments.NonZeroUnitsNetTotal;
            if (nonZeroUnitsNetTotal == null || nonZeroUnitsNetTotal === 'undefined') {
                nonZeroUnitsNetTotal = netTotal;
            }

            var nonZeroRateNetTotal = window.dialogArguments.NonZeroRateNetTotal;
            if (nonZeroRateNetTotal == null || nonZeroRateNetTotal === 'undefined') {
                nonZeroRateNetTotal = netTotal;
            }

            var negation = document.getElementById("ddlNegation").value;
            var calculatedAmount = 0;
            var netAmount = 0;

            if (AdjustByOrTo == "0") { //Adjust BY
                switch (adjustmentType) {
                    case "fixed":
                        netAmount = negation * adjustmentAmount * selectedItemsCount + netTotal;
                        break;
                    case "percent":
                        calculatedAmount = negation * netTotal * adjustmentAmount / 100;
                        calculatedAmount = roundup(calculatedAmount, 2);
                        netAmount = calculatedAmount + netTotal;
                        break;
                    case "unit":
                        calculatedAmount = negation * rate * adjustmentAmount;
                        netAmount = calculatedAmount + nonZeroRateNetTotal;
                        break;
                    case "rate":
                        calculatedAmount = negation * unit * adjustmentAmount;
                        netAmount = calculatedAmount + nonZeroUnitsNetTotal;
                        break;
                }

                if (adjustmentType == "fixed") {
                    lblCalculatedAmount.innerHTML = "";
                    lblCalculatedAmount.title = "";
                } else {
                        lblCalculatedAmount.innerHTML = formatCurr(calculatedAmount, 2);
                        lblCalculatedAmount.title = "Calculated Adjustment Amount: " + formatCurr(calculatedAmount, 9);
                    }
                }
            
            else if (AdjustByOrTo == "1") { //Adjust TO
                switch (adjustmentType) {
                    case "fixed":
                        netAmount = netTotal;
                        calculatedAmount = negation * adjustmentAmount * selectedItemsCount - netAmount;
                        break;
                    case "percent":
                        netAmount = netTotal;
                        calculatedAmount = netAmount * (negation * adjustmentAmount - 100) / 100;
                        calculatedAmount = roundup(calculatedAmount, 2);
                        break;
                    case "unit":
                        netAmount = netTotal;
                        calculatedAmount = negation * rate * adjustmentAmount - netAmount;
                        break;
                    case "rate":
                        netAmount = nonZeroUnitsNetTotal;
                        calculatedAmount = negation * unit * adjustmentAmount - netAmount;
                        break;
                }

                lblCalculatedAmount.innerHTML = formatCurr(calculatedAmount, 2);
                lblCalculatedAmount.title = "Calculated Adjustment Amount: " + formatCurr(calculatedAmount, 9);
            }

            lblNetAmount.innerHTML = formatCurr(netAmount, 2);
            lblNetAmount.title = formatCurr(netAmount, 9);
            
            if (percentOfResponsibility != null) {
                $('#lblNetAmountWithPoR').text(formatCurr(netAmount * percentOfResponsibility, 2));
            }
            
            var cssClassName = "ff-calculatedAmount";
            if (adjustmentType == "fixed") {
                $('#calculatedAmountCell').removeClass(cssClassName);
            } else {
                $('#calculatedAmountCell').addClass(cssClassName);
            }

            moveFocusTo();
        }
        function moveFocusTo() {
            if (typeof (useAccessibleNavigation) == "undefined" || !useAccessibleNavigation) {
                document.getElementById('txtAdjustmentAmount').focus();
            }
        }

        $(function() {
            var percentOfResponsibility = window.dialogArguments.PercentOfResponsibility;
            $('#NetAmountWithPoRSection').toggle(percentOfResponsibility != null);
            if (percentOfResponsibility != null) {
                var netAmount = parseFloat(window.dialogArguments.NetAmount);
                $('#lblNetAmountWithPoR').text(formatCurr(netAmount * percentOfResponsibility, 2));
            }
        });

        function roundup(num, dec) {
            dec = dec || 0;
            var s = String(num);
            if (s % 1) {
                var countDecimals = s.toString().split(".")[1].length;
                if (countDecimals == 3)
                    s = s.replace(/5$/, '6');
            }
            return Number((+s).toFixed(dec));
        }

    </script>

               function btnOK_OnClick() {
                   
            var adjustmentAmount = parseFloat(changeCurToJSSeparators(document.mainForm.txtAdjustmentAmount.value));
            var adjustmentType = document.mainForm.ddlAdjustType.value;
            var adjustByOrTo = document.mainForm.ddlAdjustByOrTo.value;
            var negation = document.mainForm.ddlNegation.value;
            var netTotal = parseFloat(window.dialogArguments.NetAmount);
            var unit = parseFloat(window.dialogArguments.Unit);
            var rate = parseFloat(window.dialogArguments.Rate);

            if(!RequiredFieldValidatorEvaluateIsValid(amountValidator))
            {
                alert(amountValidator.errormessage);
                document.mainForm.txtAdjustmentAmount.focus();
                return;
            }

            if(isNaN(adjustmentAmount))
            {
                alert('Invalid amount!');
                document.mainForm.txtAdjustmentAmount.focus();
                return;
            }

            if(adjustmentType == 'percent')
            {
                if(adjustmentAmount > 100)
                {
                    alert('The maximum amount for a percentage adjustment is 100');
                    document.mainForm.txtAdjustmentAmount.focus();
                    return;
                }
            }

            var selectedItemsCount = window.dialogArguments.SelectedItemsCount;
            if (selectedItemsCount == null || selectedItemsCount == 'undefined') 
            {
                selectedItemsCount = 1;
            }

            var nonZeroUnitsNetTotal = window.dialogArguments.NonZeroUnitsNetTotal;
            if (nonZeroUnitsNetTotal == null || nonZeroUnitsNetTotal == 'undefined') 
            {
                nonZeroUnitsNetTotal = netTotal;
            }

            var amount = 0;
            if (adjustByOrTo == '0')
            {
                switch(adjustmentType)
                {
                    case 'rate':
                        amount = negation * adjustmentAmount * unit;
                        break;
                    case 'unit':
                        amount = negation * adjustmentAmount * rate;
                        break;
                    case 'percent':
                        amount = negation * adjustmentAmount * netTotal / 100;
                        break;
                    case 'fixed':
                        amount = negation * adjustmentAmount;
                        break;
                    default:
                        return;
                }
            }
            else if(adjustByOrTo == '1')
            {
                switch(adjustmentType)
                {
                    case 'rate':
                        amount = (negation * adjustmentAmount * unit) - nonZeroUnitsNetTotal;
                        break;
                    case 'unit':
                        amount = (negation * adjustmentAmount * rate) - netTotal;
                        break;
                    case 'percent':
                        amount = (negation * adjustmentAmount * netTotal - 100) / 100;
                        break;
                    case 'fixed':
                        amount = negation * adjustmentAmount - netTotal;
                        break;
                    default:
                        return;
                }
            }
            
            if (adjustByOrTo == '0')
            {
                var totals = window.dialogArguments.ArrayTotals;
                if (totals != undefined && totals != null && (adjustmentType == 'rate' || adjustmentType == 'unit')) 
                {
                    const fieldName = adjustmentType == 'rate' ? 'units' : 'rate';
                    for (var index = 0; index < totals.length; ++index) {
                        if((totals[index].netTotal + negation * adjustmentAmount * totals[index][fieldName]) < 0)
                        {
                            alert('You cannot adjust by an amount greater than the smallest selected line item');
                            document.mainForm.txtAdjustmentAmount.focus();
                            return;
                        }
                    }
                }

                var minAmount = parseFloat(window.dialogArguments.MinAmount);
                if(!isNaN(minAmount) && adjustmentType == 'fixed' && (minAmount + negation * adjustmentAmount) < 0)
                {
                    alert('You cannot adjust by an amount greater than the smallest selected line item');
                    document.mainForm.txtAdjustmentAmount.focus();
                    return;
                }
            }
        
if((amount < -999999999999.99) || (amount > 999999999999.99)){
    alert('Invalid adjustment amount value. Valid range is -999,999,999,999.99 to 999,999,999,999.99.');
    document.mainForm.txtAdjustmentAmount.focus();
    return;
}

        currencySymbol = window.dialogArguments.CurrentCurrencySymbol;

    <script type="text/javascript">
    function CheckAllAppeals() {
        var cbAll = document.getElementById("SelectAllCheckbox");
        var grid = document.getElementById("AllAppealDataGrid");
        var checked = cbAll.checked;
        $("input[id$=SelectCheckbox][type=checkbox]", grid).each(function () { this.checked = checked; });
    }

    function UpdateHeaderCheckBox() {
        var cbAll = document.getElementById("SelectAllCheckbox");
        var grid = document.getElementById("AllAppealDataGrid");
        var checked = false;
        var indeterminate = false;
        var first = true;
        $("input[id$=SelectCheckbox][type=checkbox]", grid)
            .each(function () {
                if (first) {
                    checked = this.checked;
                    first = false;
                }
                else if (this.checked != checked) {
                    indeterminate = true;
                    return false;
                }
            });
        cbAll.indeterminate = indeterminate;
        cbAll.checked = checked;
    }

    function checkAndInformUnsavedAdjNetToChanges() {
        var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
        if (changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount > 0)
            return 'You have unsaved adjustments to this invoice. If you leave this page you will lose you adjustments!';
    }

    var onBeforeUnloadFired = false; //IE twice fires occasionally fires onbeforeunload twice. manipulation with this variable solves problem. And also uses to 'cancel' onbeforeunload

    $(document).ready(function () {

        var getUnsavedChangesScript = function () {
            var handler = checkAndInformUnsavedAdjNetToChanges;
            return function () {
                this.onbeforeunload = null; // allow to call it once, then enables handler again in mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent

                var result = handler();
                if (result) {

                    mainFrameWindow.mainFrame._getPageDisabler().hide(); //PageDisabler already shown. Need to be hidden again

                    if (T360.IsMSIE9OrLess())
                        window.parent.event.returnValue = result;

                    return result;
                }
            };
        };

        var documentIFrameWindow = $('#DocumentIFrame', mainFrameWindow.document)[0].contentWindow;

        var onBeforeUploadHandler = function () {
            documentIFrameWindow.onbeforeunload = getUnsavedChangesScript();
        };
        /* enable onbeforeunload when user clicks on main menu */
        mainFrameWindow.mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent.attach(onBeforeUploadHandler);

        var $contentPackage = parent.$(':tyMetrix-t360contentPackage');
        $contentPackage.t360contentPackage('attachBeforeGoBackEventHandler', onBeforeUploadHandler);

        /* detach all handlers in order to keep mainmenu workable */
        documentIFrameWindow.onunload = function () {
            mainFrameWindow.mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent.free();
            $contentPackage.t360contentPackage('freeBeforeGoBackEventHandler');
        };

        $('div#InvoiceLineItemSection').on('click', 'tr.PagerStyle a', function () {
            ContainerUpdater.onceOnUpdate(function () {
                var $scrollContent = $('body.MatterInvoiceDetailPage #ContentPackagePage_ScrollContent');
                $scrollContent.animate({scrollTop: $scrollContent.scrollTop() + $('table#InvoiceLineItemDataGrid').offset().top - $scrollContent.offset().top}, 1);
            });
        });

        for (var i = 0, l = ePanel.length; i < l; i++) {
            $(ePanel[i]).off('collapsed expanded').on('collapsed expanded', function (event, epanel) {
                LineItemsGridMenuButtonClickProcessor.disablePanelsTabNavigation();
            });
        }
    });

        require(["jquery"], function ($) {
            $(document).on('beforePrint.pdfOutputModule', function (event, pageClientSideModel, printOption) {
                updateDetailsPageGridModel(pageClientSideModel);
                updateDetailsPageModel(pageClientSideModel);
                updateFacetsModel(pageClientSideModel, printOption);
            });
        });

<script type="text/javascript">

function InvoiceAction(parentForm, actionCode, netAmount, minAmount, isFeesOrExpenses, restoreAccrualStyle, currentAmount,reviewerId,previousStatus,reasonCodeDescription){
    this.ParentForm = parentForm;
    this.ActionCode = actionCode;
    this.NetAmount = netAmount;
    this.MinAmount = minAmount;
    this.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeesOrExpenses;
    this.AdjustedObject = "Invoice";
    this.RestoreAccrualStyle = restoreAccrualStyle;
    this.CurrentAmount = currentAmount;
    this.ReviewerId = reviewerId;
    this.PreviousStatus = previousStatus;
    this.ReasonCodeDescription = reasonCodeDescription;
    this.Results = new function()
        {
            this.toString = function()
                {
                    var a = new Array(encodeURIComponent(this.Narrative),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.BillCodeGroupBillCodeId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentType),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.IsFeesOrExpenses),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.RestoreAccrualStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.CurrentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReviewerId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.PreviousStatus),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReasonCodeDescription));
                    return a.join('|');
                }
        }
}

function doInvoiceConfirmableInvoiceRejectAction(actionCode, total, checkAdjustNetChanges){
    var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
    if((changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount != 0) && checkAdjustNetChanges) {
        __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewRequiereConfirmSaveChanges', actionCode);
    }
    else{
        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode, total);
        invoiceAction.NetTotal = total;
        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
            if(ok){
                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode);
            }    
        });
    }
}
                    function doInvoiceConfirmableAction(actionCode, total, postBackOnCancel, isFeeExpense, percentOfResponsibility)
                    {
                        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode, total);
                        invoiceAction.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeeExpense;
                        invoiceAction.NetTotal = total;
                        invoiceAction.PercentOfResponsibility = percentOfResponsibility >= 0 ? percentOfResponsibility : 1;
                        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
                        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
                            if(ok){
                                SetScrollTop();
                                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode);
                            }
                            else if(postBackOnCancel){
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewCancelAction', actionCode);
                            }
                        });                       
                    }
                    function doAdjustToSave(actionCode, postBackOnCancel, isFeeExpense)
                    {
                        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode);
                        invoiceAction.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeeExpense;
                        invoiceAction.NetTotal = 0;
                        invoiceAction.PercentOfResponsibility = 1;
                        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
                        var controlsToUpdate = getControlsToUpdate();
                        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
                            if(ok){
                                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);
                            }
                            else if(postBackOnCancel){
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewCancelAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);
                            }
                        });                       
                    }
function doSelectedLineItemUndoAction(actionCode){
    if(checkSelected()){
        var selectedLineItems = getSelectedLineItems();
        if(g_SelectedLineItemsCounter === 1){
            $("#" + selectedLineItems[0].id.replace('chkSelect', 'btnUndoLineItemActions')).click();
            return false;
        }
        var ok = confirm('Are you sure you want to undo all review actions for the selected line items?\r\n\r\nOnly your own review actions will be undone.');
        if(ok){
            SetScrollTop();
            var controlsToUpdate = null;
            actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);
        }
    }
    else{
            alert('No line items selected.');
    }
}
                function checkUnsavedAdjNetToChanges(isRequiredConfirm, actionCode)
                {
                      if(isRequiredConfirm)
                      {
                          var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
                          if(changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount > 0)
                          {
                              __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewRequiereConfirmSaveChanges', actionCode);
                              return false;
                          }
                      }
                      return true;
                }
                function onAdjustToCancelChangesButtonClick()
                {
                  var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
                  if(changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount > 0)

                  }
                  else
                  {
                      alert('No line items adjusted.');
                  }

    <script type="text/javascript">
    function CheckAllAppeals() {
        var cbAll = document.getElementById("SelectAllCheckbox");
        var grid = document.getElementById("AllAppealDataGrid");
        var checked = cbAll.checked;
        $("input[id$=SelectCheckbox][type=checkbox]", grid).each(function () { this.checked = checked; });
    }

    function UpdateHeaderCheckBox() {
        var cbAll = document.getElementById("SelectAllCheckbox");
        var grid = document.getElementById("AllAppealDataGrid");
        var checked = false;
        var indeterminate = false;
        var first = true;
        $("input[id$=SelectCheckbox][type=checkbox]", grid)
            .each(function () {
                if (first) {
                    checked = this.checked;
                    first = false;
                }
                else if (this.checked != checked) {
                    indeterminate = true;
                    return false;
                }
            });
        cbAll.indeterminate = indeterminate;
        cbAll.checked = checked;
    }

    function checkAndInformUnsavedAdjNetToChanges() {
        var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
        if (changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount > 0)
            return 'You have unsaved adjustments to this invoice. If you leave this page you will lose you adjustments!';
    }

    var onBeforeUnloadFired = false; //IE twice fires occasionally fires onbeforeunload twice. manipulation with this variable solves problem. And also uses to 'cancel' onbeforeunload

    $(document).ready(function () {

        var getUnsavedChangesScript = function () {
            var handler = checkAndInformUnsavedAdjNetToChanges;
            return function () {
                this.onbeforeunload = null; // allow to call it once, then enables handler again in mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent

                var result = handler();
                if (result) {

                    mainFrameWindow.mainFrame._getPageDisabler().hide(); //PageDisabler already shown. Need to be hidden again

                    if (T360.IsMSIE9OrLess())
                        window.parent.event.returnValue = result;

                    return result;
                }
            };
        };

        var documentIFrameWindow = $('#DocumentIFrame', mainFrameWindow.document)[0].contentWindow;

        var onBeforeUploadHandler = function () {
            documentIFrameWindow.onbeforeunload = getUnsavedChangesScript();
        };
        /* enable onbeforeunload when user clicks on main menu */
        mainFrameWindow.mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent.attach(onBeforeUploadHandler);

        var $contentPackage = parent.$(':tyMetrix-t360contentPackage');
        $contentPackage.t360contentPackage('attachBeforeGoBackEventHandler', onBeforeUploadHandler);

        /* detach all handlers in order to keep mainmenu workable */
        documentIFrameWindow.onunload = function () {
            mainFrameWindow.mainFrame.beforeGoToEvent.free();
            $contentPackage.t360contentPackage('freeBeforeGoBackEventHandler');
        };

        $('div#InvoiceLineItemSection').on('click', 'tr.PagerStyle a', function () {
            ContainerUpdater.onceOnUpdate(function () {
                var $scrollContent = $('body.MatterInvoiceDetailPage #ContentPackagePage_ScrollContent');
                $scrollContent.animate({scrollTop: $scrollContent.scrollTop() + $('table#InvoiceLineItemDataGrid').offset().top - $scrollContent.offset().top}, 1);
            });
        });

        for (var i = 0, l = ePanel.length; i < l; i++) {
            $(ePanel[i]).off('collapsed expanded').on('collapsed expanded', function (event, epanel) {
                LineItemsGridMenuButtonClickProcessor.disablePanelsTabNavigation();
            });
        }
    });

        require(["jquery"], function ($) {
            $(document).on('beforePrint.pdfOutputModule', function (event, pageClientSideModel, printOption) {
                updateDetailsPageGridModel(pageClientSideModel);
                updateDetailsPageModel(pageClientSideModel);
                updateFacetsModel(pageClientSideModel, printOption);
            });
        });

function InvoiceAction(parentForm, actionCode, netAmount, minAmount, isFeesOrExpenses, restoreAccrualStyle, currentAmount,reviewerId,previousStatus,reasonCodeDescription){
    this.ParentForm = parentForm;
    this.ActionCode = actionCode;
    this.NetAmount = netAmount;
    this.MinAmount = minAmount;
    this.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeesOrExpenses;
    this.AdjustedObject = "Invoice";
    this.RestoreAccrualStyle = restoreAccrualStyle;
    this.CurrentAmount = currentAmount;
    this.ReviewerId = reviewerId;
    this.PreviousStatus = previousStatus;
    this.ReasonCodeDescription = reasonCodeDescription;
    this.Results = new function()
        {
            this.toString = function()
                {
                    var a = new Array(encodeURIComponent(this.Narrative),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.BillCodeGroupBillCodeId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentType),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.AdjustmentStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.IsFeesOrExpenses),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.RestoreAccrualStyle),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.CurrentAmount),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReviewerId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.PreviousStatus),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReasonCodeDescription));
                    return a.join('|');
                }
        }
}

function doInvoiceConfirmableInvoiceRejectAction(actionCode, total, checkAdjustNetChanges){
    var changes = getAdjustNetToChanges();
    if((changes.FeeCount + changes.ExpenseCount != 0) && checkAdjustNetChanges) {
        __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewRequiereConfirmSaveChanges', actionCode);
    }
    else{
        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode, total);
        invoiceAction.NetTotal = total;
        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
            if(ok){
                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                __doPostBack('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode);
            }    
        });
    }
}
                    function doInvoiceConfirmableAction(actionCode, total, postBackOnCancel, isFeeExpense, percentOfResponsibility)
                    {
                        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode, total);
                        invoiceAction.IsFeesOrExpenses = isFeeExpense;
                        invoiceAction.NetTotal = total;
                        invoiceAction.PercentOfResponsibility = percentOfResponsibility >= 0 ? percentOfResponsibility : 1;
                        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
                        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
                            if(ok){
                                SetScrollTop();
                                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode);
                            }
                            else if(postBackOnCancel){
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewCancelAction', actionCode);
                            }
                        });                       
                    }

                    {
                        var invoiceAction = new InvoiceAction(window.form, actionCode);

                        invoiceAction.NetTotal = 0;
                        invoiceAction.PercentOfResponsibility = 1;
                        var theInvoiceActionParameters = $('#InvoiceActionParameters').get(0);
                        var controlsToUpdate = getControlsToUpdate();
                        openDialog(invoiceAction, 0, function(ok){
                            if(ok){
                                theInvoiceActionParameters.value = invoiceAction.Results;
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);
                            }
                            else if(postBackOnCancel){
                                actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewCancelAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);

function doSelectedLineItemUndoAction(actionCode){
    if(checkSelected()){
        var selectedLineItems = getSelectedLineItems();
        if(g_SelectedLineItemsCounter === 1){
            $("#" + selectedLineItems[0].id.replace('chkSelect', 'btnUndoLineItemActions')).click();
            return false;
        }
        var ok = confirm('Are you sure you want to undo all review actions for the selected line items?\r\n\r\nOnly your own review actions will be undone.');
        if(ok){
            SetScrollTop();
            var controlsToUpdate = null;
            actionDoScript('InvoiceReviewAction', actionCode, controlsToUpdate);
        }
    }
    else{
            alert('No line items selected.');
    }
}

    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
            var contentPackage = parent.$(':tyMetrix-t360contentPackage');
            contentPackage.t360contentPackage('routeToolbarFunctionalityToDetails');
        });

        $(function () {
            EPanel.delegates.toggle = function (isExpanded) {
                var count = $('.n-epanel.toggle-mode:visible').length;
                var splitter = window.parent.$("#cpVerticalSplitter").data("kendoSplitter");
                if (typeof splitter != "undefined") {
                    if (count === 0) {
                        splitter.size("#paneTop", "60px");
                    } else if (isExpanded == 1 && count === 1) {
                        splitter.size("#paneTop", "50%");
                    }
                }
            }

            for (var i = 0, l = ePanel.length; i < l; i++) {
                $(ePanel[i]).off('collapsed expanded').on('collapsed', function (event, epanel) {
                    $(epanel.panel).parents('.group-layout-container').hide();
                }).on('expanded', function (event, epanel) {
                    $(epanel.panel).parents('.group-layout-container').show();
                });
            }
        });

        require(["jquery"], function ($) {
            $(document).on('beforePrint.pdfOutputModule', function (event, pageClientSideModel) {
                updateExpandedTextAreas(pageClientSideModel);
                updateSummaryPageGridModel(pageClientSideModel);
                updateSummaryPageModel(pageClientSideModel);
            });

    this.ActionCode = actionCode;
    this.NetAmount = netAmount;

    this.AdjustedObject = "Invoice";

    this.CurrentAmount = currentAmount;

                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReviewerId),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.PreviousStatus),
                                      encodeURIComponent(this.ReasonCodeDescription));
                    return a.join('|');
                }
        }
}

    <script type="text/javascript">
        function LoginPage_OnLoad() {

            document.getElementById('screenResolution').value = "'" + screen.width + 'x' + screen.height + "'";

            //focus redirection
            var loginTextBox = window.document._all("LoginTextBox");
            var LoginPanel = window.document._all("LoginPanel");
            if (typeof (loginTextBox) != 'undefined' && loginTextBox != null) {
                LoginPanel.style.display = "";
                loginTextBox.focus();
            }
        }

        var key;

        function GetRandomSalt(callback) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "LoginPage.aspx/GetRandomSalt",
                data: "{}",
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                async: "true",
                success: function (randomSalt) {
                    callback(randomSalt.d);
                }
            });
        }

        function ValidateForm(sender) {
            try {
                if (!Page_ClientValidate()) {
                    window.focus();
                    return false;
                }

                sender.disabled = true;

                if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginSSOButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginSSOButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SaveButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("CancelButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(ChangePasswordCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("AskQuestions_SubmitQuestionsButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("AskQuestions_cancelQuestionsButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(AnswerSecurityQuestionsCallback);
            }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_BtnSubmit")) {
                    document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_btnCancel").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(SetupSecurityQuestionsCallback);
                }
            }
            finally {
                return false;        //ensure no postback
            }
        }

        function SwitchOffSsoValidation() {
            if (!/\S+/.test(window.document._all("LoginSSOTextBox").value) &&
                !/\S+/.test(window.document._all("PasswordSSOTextBox").value) &&
                /\S+/.test(window.document._all("NetworkSSOTextBox").value)) {
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("LoginSSOTextBoxValidator");
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("PasswordSSOTextBoxValidator");
            }
        }

        $(function () {
            if (T360.IsMSIE7OrLess()) {
                $(window).resize(function () { $('.Document').height($('.Document').parent().height()); });
                $(window).resize();
                $('.DisclaimerText').css('position', 'absolute');
            }
            if ($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height()) {
                $(window).resize(function () {
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height(0);
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height());
                });
                $(window).resize();
            }
            if ($('td.tdCenter').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdCenter').offset().top) {
                $('div.accountAgreement').addClass('eqie10');
            }
        });
    </script>
